dcterms:description: The peripheral nerve ultrasound dataset consists of images collected from two different anatomical structures: the peroneal nerve and the ulnar nerve. It includes 1234 images of the ulnar nerve and 410 images of the peroneal nerve, with varying anatomical regions.
dcterms:title: Peripheral nerve ultrasound images
